high_descs: move to the left a bit to face the kitchen sink
grab the butter knife out of the kitchen sink
slice the tomato to the left of the kitchen sink
place the knife in the kitchen sink
grab a tomato slice off of the kitchen counter to the left of the sink
turn right and walk over to the fridge on the left
place the tomato slice inside of the fridge, let it cool, then pick it back up and close the door
turn left and walk over to the microwave ahead
place the tomato slice inside of the microwave
anns.task_desc: place a cooled tomato slice inside of the microwave

high_descs: Turn left and head to the sink on the right.
Take the knife from the sink.
Slice the tomato on the left.
Put the knife back in the sink.
Take a slice from the tomato on the left.
Turn right and face the fridge on your left.
Open the fridge, put the tomato slice in the top box on the left, close the fridge, open the fridge back up, take the tomato slice out of the box on the left and close the fridge.
Turn left and head towards the microwave.
Open the microwave, put the tomato slice inside the microwave and close the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Heat up a tomato slice in a microwave.

high_descs: Turn left and go to the sink.
Pick up the knife that is in the sink.
Use the knife to slice the tomato that is on the left of the sink.
Place the knife back in the sink.
Pick up a slice of tomato.
Turn right and go to the refrigerator.
Place the tomato slice in the top drawer of the refrigerator and leave it in there for a few seconds before taking it back out.
Turn left and go to the microwave.
Put the tomato slice on the plate in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled tomato slice in the microwave.
